          "level": 4,
          "body": "| Present Perfect | Present Perfect Continuous |\n| --- | --- |\n| Quan tâm **kết quả**: *She **has written** three reports.* | Quan tâm **quá trình**: *She **has been writing** reports all morning.* |\n| *I **have read** the book.* (đã đọc xong) | *I **have been reading** the book.* (đang đọc, có thể chưa xong) |\n| *He **has built** the house.* (đã xây xong) | *He **has been building** the house.* (đang xây dở) |"
