          "level": 3,
          "body": "**Hướng dẫn:** Chuyển từ gốc thành dạng đúng theo ngữ cảnh.\n\n**Câu 1:** The company's annual ____ (grow) exceeded expectations this year.\n(A) grows\n(B) growth\n(C) growing\n(D) growths\n\n**Câu 2:** All applicants must meet the minimum ____ (qualify) requirements.\n(A) qualify\n(B) qualification\n(C) qualifications\n(D) qualified\n\n**Câu 3:** The new system is much more ____ (efficiency) than the previous one.\n(A) efficient\n(B) efficiently\n(C) efficiency\n(D) inefficients\n\n**Câu 4:** The board made a ____ (decide) to expand operations in Asia.\n(A) decided\n(B) decision\n(C) decisive\n(D) decisions\n\n**Câu 5:** Her presentation skills are highly ____ (impress).\n(A) impression\n(B) impressions\n(C) impressive\n(D) impressively"
