          "level": 3,
          "body": "| # | Từ/Cụm từ | Nghĩa | Ví dụ trong câu |\n| --- | --- | --- | --- |\n| 1 | **running late** | đang chậm trễ | \"I'm running late for the meeting.\" |\n| 2 | **back up** | sao lưu / dự phòng | \"Please back up your files before the update.\" |\n| 3 | **set up** | thiết lập / cài đặt | \"Can you set up the projector?\" |\n| 4 | **follow up** | theo dõi / tiếp tục | \"I'll follow up on that request tomorrow.\" |\n| 5 | **pick up** | đón / nhận | \"I'll pick up the documents on my way.\" |\n| 6 | **go over** | xem xét lại | \"Let's go over the contract one more time.\" |\n| 7 | **look into** | điều tra / tìm hiểu | \"I'll look into the issue right away.\" |\n| 8 | **put off** | hoãn lại | \"The meeting has been put off until Friday.\" |\n| 9 | **break down** | hỏng / phân tích | \"The car broke down on the highway.\" |\n| 10 | **come up with** | nghĩ ra | \"She came up with a great marketing idea.\" |\n| 11 | **get along with** | hòa thuận với | \"She gets along well with her colleagues.\" |\n| 12 | **deal with** | xử lý / giải quyết | \"He's good at dealing with difficult clients.\" |\n| 13 | **count on** | dựa vào / tin tưởng | \"You can count on me for support.\" |\n| 14 | **stand by** | sẵn sàng / chờ đợi | \"Please stand by for further instructions.\" |\n| 15 | **figure out** | tìm ra / hiểu được | \"I can't figure out how to solve this problem.\" |\n\n---"
